The '''Regional Sector Number Four's All-Human Free-For-All''' was a [[Gladiator/Legends|gladiator]] event held on [[Jubilar/Legends|Jubilar]] in [[12 BBY/Legends|12 BBY]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] won by defeating three larger combatants. Han also saw [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] for the first time. The venue had moved on from the [[Victory Forum]] where it was held or was defunct by [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

